HEADWORD: Interequinoctial
<hw>In`ter*e`qui*noc"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Coming
between the equinoxes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Summer and winter I have called <qex>interequinoctial</qex>
intervals.</q> <rj><qau>F. Balfour.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interess</ent>⟦br⟧
